Christian Fellowship Center (CFCFC) desire to aggressively help them attain.&nbsp;<a href="[~7~]">Click for more details</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p class="clearfix">Getting and remaining debt free is wise stewardship of our finances<strong>.&nbsp; </strong>Therefore, if you use a credit card for making a donation to CFCFC, we encourage you to pay the credit card bill in total to avoid any finance charges.<br /><br />Debit card use for contributions is similar to writing a check but is a faster transaction since it is done electronically. Debit cards directly access your checking account and thus there are no finance charges incurred. </p><h3>Paypal Instructions</h3><p>To make donations with Paypal you can click the button displayed below.  You do not have to register with Paypal if you don't already have an account.  First, enter the amount of donation you would like to provide in the field below Donation Amount and click the Update Total button.   Next Click the Continue link, to the left of hte Log In to Paypal box.   Next fill out your Credit Card information, <strong>Your personal information will be handled by the secure Paypal system and will not be displayed or sent to Christ First Christian Fellowship Center</strong>.  Once complete, select the &quot;review donation and continue&quot; button.  Review your information and submit.</p>{{PaypalDonateButton}} <br /><h3>To Donate by Check </h3><p>Make Check Payable to CFCFC<br />Mailing Address:<br />P.O. Box 554<br />Cary, NC 27512<br /><br /><em>All contributions are tax deductible</em> </p><p>Need more info? Please contact the church office&nbsp;at 919-851-5540. </p>";s:8:"richtext";s:1:"1";s:8:"template";s:1:"4";s:9:"menuindex";s:1:"2";s:10:"searchable";s:1:"1";s:9:"cacheable";s:1:"1";s:9:"createdby";s:1:"1";s:9:"createdon";s:10:"1211072877";s:8:"editedby";s:1:"1";s:8:"editedon";s:10:"1254882570";s:7:"deleted";s:1:"0";s:9:"deletedon";s:1:"0";s:9:"deletedby";s:1:"0";s:11:"publishedon";s:10:"1215572496";s:11:"publis