		<h1>Online Giving</h1>
		<p>Christ First Christian Fellowship Center (CFCFC) now offers the convenience of online giving. You can contribute to our ministries using either your credit or debit card. Online giving is easy, fast, safe and secure.<br /><br />You can do a &quot;one-time&quot; gift or sign-up to make your online giving regular and automatic.&nbsp; For CFCFC members, your contributions will appear on your annual statement. </p><p>Online giving allows you to support our ministry no matter where you are. According to <strong>Luke 6:38</strong>, your faithful giving stimulates the hearts of men to give unto you in such a way that it shall run over so that you can continue to be a blessing to others. </p><blockquote>		<!--		<p>		-->&quot;Give, and it shall be given unto you; good measure, pressed down, and shaken together, and running over, shall men give into your bosom. For with the same measure that ye mete withal it shall be measured to you again&quot;.&nbsp; <!--		</p>		--></blockquote><!--<cite>Luke 6:38</cite> --><p class="clearfix">&nbsp;</p><h3>Capital Campaign Pledge</h3><p>Our nation is facing an epidemic of youth turning from their Christ-centered roots and joining gangs and committing suicide at an alarming rate never before experienced in our life time. &nbsp;God has revealed to me that this is primarily due to a lack of motivation by the church to aggressively go after our youth and secondly because our youth do not understand that they have a predestined future. &nbsp;They have a predetermined, God given purpose that we at Christ First Christian Fellowship Center (CFCFC) desire to aggressively help them attain.&nbsp;<a href="[~7~]">Click for more details</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p class="clearfix">Getting and remaining debt free is wise stewardship of our finances<strong>.&nbsp; </strong>Therefore, if you use a credit card for making a donation to CFCFC, we encourage you to pay the credit card bill in total to avoid any finance charges.<br /><br />Debit card use for contributions is similar to writing a check but is a faster transaction since it is done electronically. Debit cards directly access your checking account and thus there are no finance charges incurred. </p><h3>Paypal Instructions</h3><p>To make donations with Paypal you can click the button displayed below.  You do not have to register with Paypal if you don't already have an account.  First, enter the amount of donation you would like to provide in the field below Donation Amount and click the Update Total button.   Next Click the Continue link, to the left of hte Log In to Paypal box.   Next fill out your Credit Card information, <strong>Your personal information will be handled by the secure Paypal system and will not be displayed or sent to Christ First Christian Fellowship Center</strong>.  Once complete, select the &quot;review donation and continue&quot; button.  Review your information and submit.</p><form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post">
